Use this updated stripper instead of the one included in the diablo_v4.rar

_sText:
ze_diablo_v4_1
---------------------------------------
1 Playable Human Item
1 Playable Zombie Item
3 Bosses
6 stages (3 Normal, 3 Extreme)
4 NPC's
Lasers
---------------------------------------

The definitive ze_diablo experience with all major issues fixed!

Differences from v3:
-All bugs fixed
-3 new stages (Extreme)
-Quality of life improvements
-Updated visuals

Special thanks to Hobbitten for immense support with the logic systems and models!

This map uses a lot of assets from other maps and a lot of custom assets.
Assets from this map are to be used anywhere.

This map is allowed to be played anywhere.

This map is allowed to be ported anywhere.
